Package: pclvbayes
Title: Bayesian Pairwise compositional Lotka-Volterra
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(person(given="Gyeongjun", family="Cho",
    email="chogj88@korea.kr", role=c("aut","cre"),
    comment=c(ORCID="0000-0001-6820-2969",
              affiliation="National Institute of Agricultural Sciences",
              country="Korea, Republic of")),
    person(given="Rural Development Administration (RDA)", role="cph"),
    person(given="National Institute of Agricultural Sciences (NAS)", role="cph"))
Description: Implements Bayesian pairwise generalized Lotka–Volterra (gLV)-inspired regressions for microbiome time-series from amplicon sequencing. Residuals are OU (≈AR(1)) or white-noise with Δt-aware options; includes optional correlation-based screening, tidy edge reshaping, Kalman ELPD for OU, and diagnostics; uses cmdstanr/CmdStan.
